text: Anoectochilus zhejiangensis is a species of plant in the family Orchidaceae. It is endemic to China (Fujian, Guangxi, and Zhejiang provinces).Kew World Checklist of Selected Plant FamiliesFlora of China v 25 p 79, 浙江金线兰 zhe jiang jin xian lan, Anoectochilus zhejiangensis == References == ==External links== *China Plant Specialist Group. 2004.
